videos.headline: D.J. Uiagalelei runs it in for Clemson TD
videos.description: D.J. Uiagalelei takes the snap and runs into the end zone to score a 4-yard Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (D.J. Uiagalelei runs it in for Clemson TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Will Shipley's TD puts Clemson up 14-0
videos.description: Will Shipley gets the handoff and navigates to the outside to score a 7-yard touchdown to give Clemson a 14-0 lead over South Carolina State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Will Shipley's TD puts Clemson up 14-0) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kobe Pace powers his way to Clemson TD
videos.description: Kobe Pace takes the handoff and fights his way in to score a short 2-yard touchdown for Clemson.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kobe Pace powers his way to Clemson TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Justyn Ross leaps to score Clemson TD
videos.description: D.J. Uiagalelei connects with Justyn Ross who leaps to make the catch and score an 11-yard Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Justyn Ross leaps to score Clemson TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: D.J. Uiagalelei keeps it to score 2nd rushing TD
videos.description: D. Uiagalelei keeps the snap and shoots his way through traffic to score a 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (D.J. Uiagalelei keeps it to score 2nd rushing TD) 2021/09/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Will Shipley muscles his way to 13-yard Clemson TD
videos.description: Will Shipley scores his second rushing touchdown of the night as he fights his way through defenders to score a 13-yard Clemson touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Will Shipley muscles his way to 13-yard Clemson TD) 2021/9/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taisun Phommachanh finds Lyn-J Dixon for 14-yard TD
videos.description: Taisun Phommachanh completes a pass to Lyn-J Dixon who slips through defenders to score a 14-yard touchdown for Clemson.
